data.name: iamjakehill
data.bio: Jake Hill is an American rapper, singer and songwriter from south Alabama. Combining HipHop and metalcore elements, he has amassed a large online following by using his own personal hardships and experiences as a way to connect with like-minded supporters across the globe. data.name: Leyla Blue
data.bio: Leyla Blue is an American pop and R&B singer and songwriter based in New York. She has made several viral hits and has amassed a large following on TikTok. Read more on Last.fm. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply.
